05)--------ProjectionExec: expr=[price@2 as price, __mr_is_last_match_row@7 as __mr_is_last_match_row], schema=[price:Int32;N, __mr_is_last_match_row:Boolean]
06)----------MatchRecognizePatternExec: pattern=Concat([Symbol(Start), Symbol(Named("A"))]), schema=[company:Utf8View;N, price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N, __mr_symbol_A:Boolean;N, __mr_classifier:Utf8, __mr_match_number:UInt64, __mr_match_sequence_number:UInt64, __mr_is_last_match_row:Boolean, __mr_is_included_row:Boolean]
07)------------ProjectionExec: expr=[company@0 as company, price_date@1 as price_date, price@2 as price, price@2 > 100 as __mr_symbol_A], schema=[company:Utf8View;N, price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N, __mr_symbol_A:Boolean;N]
08)--------------DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[0], schema=[company:Utf8View;N, price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N]

